  "ruleset_id": 14349281,
  "ruleset_name": "Protect main",
  "notes": [
    "This file records the live GitHub ruleset before the solo-owner adjustment and the agreed target policy after the adjustment.",
    "When another contributor is added, consider raising required_approving_review_count from 0 to 1."
